children.name: SELECT "shipping_weightband"."id", "shipping_weightband"."method_id", "shipping_weightband"."upper_limit", "shipping_weightband"."charge" FROM "shipping_weightband" WHERE ("shipping_weightband"."method_id" = 25 AND "shipping_weightband"."upper_limit" < 1) ORDER BY "shipping_weightband"."upper_limit" DESC
